<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Refund Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Refund Eligibility</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We offer refunds in the following cases:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Damaged or defective products</li>
                <li>Wrong items delivered</li>
                <li>Expired products</li>
                <li>Order cancellation before shipping</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Refund Process</h2>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Initiate refund request within 7 days of delivery</li>
                <li>Provide order details and reason for refund</li>
                <li>Return product in original packaging (if applicable)</li>
                <li>Refund processed within 5-7 business days</li>
                <li>Amount credited to original payment method</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Non-Refundable Items</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Opened medicines or healthcare products</li>
                <li>Personal care items</li>
                <li>Items marked as non-returnable</li>
                <li>Products damaged by customer</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Refund Methods</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Original payment method refund</li>
                <li>Store credit (optional)</li>
                <li>Bank transfer (in special cases)</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">Note: Shipping charges are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> 